snippet.title: All Over v0.8.06 - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
An indie Action RPG/adventure/puzzle Complete story-based quests, solve puzzles, use your sword and spells to fight and gain loot from monsters. Gather resources to build and craft potions and items. Fight legendary bosses.
